{"tid":134520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"28歲內地男金鐘月台候車 從後非禮52歲女","createTime":"2017-02-25T14:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T16:22:27.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1431d42b89a53f6324623be421340587ac757375","tid":134520,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:07:21.000Z","msg":"<strong>28歲內地男金鐘月台候車 從後非禮52歲女</strong><br />\n<br />\n2017-02-25 17:43:49 HKT  <br />\n         <br />\n港鐵金鐘站下午發生非禮案。一名52歲婦人，今早9時許繁忙時間在金鐘港鐵站月台等候上車期間，聲稱被一名男子從後非禮，由職員代為報警。警方接報到場調查，以涉嫌非禮拘捕28歲姓張內地男子，帶返警署調查，案件交由中區警區刑事調查隊第4隊跟進。"},{"pid":"ed331683a398cd9fd7a4835ca1805c1c0acae80b","tid":134520,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:08:23.000Z","msg":"我見妳婆婆好得喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ebd2cf98a0e8f9cced7ca64262717437ffd56d","tid":134520,"uid":36142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:09:12.000Z","msg":"少女我唔鋤愛阿婆"},{"pid":"13d3f086c618883bc52d53231a3af2fa1ad3028e","tid":134520,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b64a4eb16bcfd712943a950c8e0bc809eef0ca","tid":134520,"uid":15866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:25:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>少女我唔鋤愛阿婆</blockquote><br />\n驅風煲老藕搭得過"},{"pid":"ea08b3d99632e74548259ad6999d2d6b446fb67e","tid":134520,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:25:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed13ddfeb7e1ed992fb441734e84295a5fc20532","tid":134520,"uid":42452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"又黎D ON9回覆想搞到件事望落冇乜野"},{"pid":"443fb90671200bf2048dc79f842a1f0e3d05715b","tid":134520,